{"tid":2211140,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"命理師見小鬼靈堂照驚呼：糟了！通靈後「背後原因」曝光","createTime":"2020-09-21T02:41:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T13:44:05.000Z","uid":148652,"like":0,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5a1908deb4c97124f62f2b4fda70a88c390539a0","tid":2211140,"uid":148652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T02:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RuyMQJf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRuyMQJf.jpg&h=9bd15621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n藝人「小鬼」黃鴻升16日驚傳在北投住處過世，享年36歲，消息曝光後，讓許多圈內好友與粉絲都相當不捨；昨（20）日是小鬼靈堂開放的第2天，湧入大批演藝圈人士、好友和許多粉絲前往哀悼。不過，通靈大師江嘉葉看到「靈堂一幕」卻直言糟糕了。<br />\n<br />\n小鬼的靈堂設置於民權東路二段龍巖A館，從19日至21日上午10點至下午6點開放親友前往弔唁，期間除了女友峮峮一路守候，還有許多演藝圈好友和粉絲也前來哀悼，可以看出小鬼生前的好人緣。靈堂照片上，小鬼身著白色襯衫仰望天空的側臉，配上白色鮮花，象徵「真誠不變的愛」以及「永恆」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，根據《三立新聞》報導，通靈大師江嘉葉看到小鬼遺照後，驚覺不對勁，直言小鬼躲在照片右下角，看起來十分虛弱且驚恐，<br />\n<br />\n江嘉葉通靈過後透露，神明指出小鬼的魂魄尚未完全引來靈堂，有6分還留在遺體那，需透過小鬼的親友趕快處理，請祂跟著一起來到靈堂，否則魂魄不全是不吉利的。"},{"pid":"de3f4da0571f042d083be08e319f2d15085d9aea","tid":2211140,"uid":58445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T02:53:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"444d79d3e0c658777ff5f3c274fb33b350197918","tid":2211140,"uid":292789,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T03:01:53.000Z","msg":"呢D神棍幾時死"},{"pid":"c1f6970ad54321dd10abbec9981dab26f2e8d9f8","tid":2211140,"uid":4811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T03:06:47.000Z","msg":"台灣佬好多神棍迷信撚"},{"pid":"0690153b9fd32f5f648880c1a76c80c0cbca88bb","tid":2211140,"uid":78995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T03:11:59.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">否則魂魄不全是不吉利的</span><br />\n<br />\n哦，原來只係不吉利啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d269b2f1a5befb52cf3df4f28104f39a232758c2","tid":2211140,"uid":107405,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T03:16:38.000Z","msg":"命理師江嘉葉日前受訪提到「韓有總統命格」，更鐵口斷「他90%會當總統」<br />\n<br />\n以面相學來說，江嘉葉表示「韓有大富大貴命，額頭寬宥亮，顴骨有利，鼻子挺鼻骨很正，且下巴圓潤，後腦杓的枕骨突出，前凸、後凸格局都會不錯」。要有總統命必須具備九五至尊，江點出「韓國瑜頭頂相平有氣，有龍骨是很少有人有的」，郭台銘則沒有龍骨，只能留在民間當王。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0941e4fa2a9a0a906fc9201c1d6ca7fc105157","tid":2211140,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d269b2f1a5befb52cf3df4f28104f39a232758c2","tid":2211140,"uid":107405,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T03:16:38.000Z","msg":"命理師江嘉葉日前受訪提到「韓有總統命格」，更鐵口斷「他90%會當總統」<br />\n<br />\n以面相學來說，江嘉葉表示「韓有大富大貴命，額頭寬宥亮，顴骨有利，鼻子挺鼻骨很正，且下巴圓潤，後腦杓的枕骨突出，前凸、後凸格局都會不錯」。要有總統命必須具備九五至尊，江點出「韓國瑜頭頂相平有氣，有龍骨是很少有人有的」，郭台銘則沒有龍骨，只能留在民間當王。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i